{"type": "article", "id": 7942, "title": "Focus 桌面分隔屏", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-31T07:19:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234503RVz04XMEIpkvDJgi.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t现代人对于隐私的要求无处不在，Focus 正是针对此需求而设计的。这是一个桌面分隔屏，把它放在桌子上，便可以划出一个暂时的私人区域。折叠式的设计使得它十分便于携带，对于咖啡厅，图书馆等去处，看起来都是蛮不错的选择。这款产品有两种尺寸，一种适于单人，而另一种长款可以绕过更大的桌子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234500lBDgkEuGxjQbPLfC.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234501GR1IrvK5NyQzC4AB.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234501sTeuviWSr02fPqXk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234502TUMEx15uF4dp60Qb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.65520833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}